{
  "stem": "11552.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But some of the passenger cars were filled with SS Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The Partisans, the Kovpak partisans found out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they, and they blew up those cars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there was a massacre there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then, somebody opened the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we ran out into the ditch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And while I was running, I got a piece of shrapnel in two places-- in one in my leg in here in-- and in my tush.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I still have the piece there inside me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were in that ditch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then they gathered up all the boys and girls and put us in, in, in-- downstairs in the basement in basement room in the prison.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they were going to check the documents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Because they believed that it was somebody from this train that told the Partisans that there are Germans in the car-- all kind of story.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then I thought I was in terrible trouble.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Because, you see, I didn't have any documents to identify who I was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And who doesn't have documents and the way I was dressed, I wasn't really looking like a girl going to Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And so I told, told them a story that I ran away from my cruel stepmother, and that I left my little brother, and that I should get out of here.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a little window, which was very difficult to open.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they opened that window, which [? fall-- ?] the window opened inside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can you imagine what kind of terrible thing it is?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, they heaved me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I crawled out of this window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was already wounded, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I was crawling, I looked in in another window.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I saw there people wearing khaki with bandages all over them.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
